OL,5, Trainee pilots who lost tens of        
OL,6, thousands of pounds when their flying  
OL,7, schools collapsed are calling on the   
OL,8, aviation regulator to take action.     
OL,10,FThree UK flying schools have closed in 
OL,11,F2023, leaving students who had paid    
OL,12,Ffees in advance facing heavy losses.   
OL,14,FThe British Airline Pilots Association 
OL,15,Fand Wings Alliance, which represents   
OL,16,Fstudent pilots, are leading a campaign.
OL,18,FThe Civil Aviation Authority (CAA),    
OL,19,Fwhich oversees flying schools, said it 
OL,20,Fwas "looking carefully at the issues". 
